node.text: I had my last surgery today at Vanderbilt Hospital! I can’t brag about them enough. They are the absolute best! I had the pins removed from my left finger and it turns out I still had a piece of metal in my face! I’m so happy to be completely done with surgeries. All I have to do now is keep healing. A big thank you again to the team at Vanderbilt and a big thank you to my lovely wife for being there for me every step of the way ❤️.
